## Enforcement Cadence

**Daily**: Automated linters in CI
**Weekly**: Doc-gardening agent scans for violations
**On-demand**: Before major releases, run full audit

## Violation Remediation

When violations found:
1. Doc-gardening agent opens PR with fix
2. PR includes:
   - What violated the principle
   - Why the principle exists
   - How the fix enforces it
3. Reviewer (human or agent) verifies fix maintains functionality
4. Auto-merge if tests pass + approved
